data.description: Welcome home to this newly built craftsman Ranch beauty located on the tee box of the 9th and 29th holes of Mallards Edge and just 15 minutes from SouthPark Mall and highways.  This maintenance free home offers 3 bedrooms on the main floor along with first floor laundry and dining.  Enjoy the covered patio with views of the course, woods and ponds to sip your morning coffee.  The finished industrial look of the lower level has an entertainment area, full wet bar with automatic glass washer, luxury vinyl flooring, an additional room w/egressed window that can be used as a 4th bedroom and a Full bath!  You will also find ample craft and storage in the unfinished area. Home features: Gas fireplace in main living room, electric fireplace in finished rec room, Ihome smart system, trayed ceilings, double head roman shower, granite throughout.  Inquire about extensive coverage of the Builders warranty that remains in effect until 12/31/23.
